      <title>日本邮政与保险公司一起因收益率较低而推迟债券购买</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-21/japan-post-joins-insurers-delaying-bond-buying-on-lower-yields</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本邮政保险公司与其他主要人寿保险公司一样，在收益率上升之前暂缓购买国内主权债券，因为人们一直猜测世界上最后一个低于零的利率政策将在今年晚些时候结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-21/japan-post-joins-insurers-delaying-bond-buying-on-lower-yields</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 23:02:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
